      {"n": 2, "text": "Confirm Endorsement 4A on the declarations page and prior loss on the policy history.", "source": "policy master"},
      {"n": 3, "text": "Set reserve to the median outcome for this pattern (approx. $60–75k first cut). Mark review Day 10 and Day 30.", "source": "int_2025_04_22"},
      {"n": 4, "text": "Hold ALE conservative for the first 10 days. Communicate this to insured directly by phone.", "source": "int_2025_04_22"},
      {"n": 5, "text": "Issue Reservation of Rights letter and call the insured to explain before the letter arrives.", "source": "int_2025_04_15"},
      {"n": 6, "text": "Courtesy notify SIU. Not because of suspicion — because of exposure size.", "source": "int_2025_04_15"},
      {"n": 7, "text": "On origin report, cross-check panel model against active manufacturer recall list.", "source": "CL-105619, CL-106861"},
      {"n": 8, "text": "If in recall window, open subrogation and preserve the panel as evidence.", "source": "int_2025_04_22"},
      {"n": 9, "text": "When origin clears, release ROR same day and call insured with the news.", "source": "int_2025_04_15"}
